                              </foreign>
                           </desc>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a3">
                          <locus target="#iiv(erso) #iiir(ecto) #iiiv(erso) #ivr(ecto)" facs="003 003 004 004">Fols. iiv(erso), iiir(ecto), iiiv(erso), ivr(ecto)</locus>
                           <desc type="Asmat">
                               Asmat prayer told to Saint Andrew by our Lord when he sent him to a cannibalistic people to deliver Matthias.Incipit: <foreign xml:lang="gez">በስመ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/>  አስማት፡ ዘነገሮ፡ እግዚአነ፡ ለቅዱስ፡ እንድርያስ፡ ረድ፡ ሐዋርያ፡ ወሰማዕት፡ <gap reason="omitted"/>  ወይቤሎ፡ ሁር፡ ሀገረ፡ በላእተ፡ ሰብእ፡ ኀበ፡ ሐሎ፡ እሁከ፡ ማትያስ፡ ከመ፡ ታውጽኦ፡ እምቤተ፤ ሞቅህ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/></foreign>
